Nigeria to Produce Iron Ore From Itakpe in 2012, Reuters Reports

-- B y   V i n c e n t   N w a n m a
-- 
2011-09-02T11:14:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-02/nigeria-to-produce-iron-ore-from-itakpe-in-2012-reuters-reports.html
Nigeria expects to start significant
production at the Itakpe iron-ore deposits next year, Reuters
reported, citing Trade and Investment Minister Olusegun Aganga.  Itakpe contains 3 billion metric tons of iron-ore reserves,
the news agency cited Aganga as saying. Initial output will be 2
million tons annually, Reuters  reported .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Vincent Nwanma in Lagos at 
 vnwanma@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 